title: Masked Singer Sverige
overview: Twelve well-known people, hidden under fabulous masks, compete in one of the most spectacular singing contests ever. Who is taking part is super secret and not even host David Hellenius knows who they are. The panel includes none other than Pernilla Wahlgren, Måns Zelmerlöw, Felix Herngren and Nour El Refai, whose task is to figure out which celebrity is hiding behind the mask.
